Given this political fundraising email, respond with the name of the committee in the disclaimer that begins with Paid for by but does not include Paid for by, the committee address or the treasurer name. If no committee is present, return "None". Do not include any other text, no yapping.
name: Barbra Streisand
email: info@defeatboebertpac.com
subject: No one has ever regretted getting off the sidelines
body: Peter, I’m an actress, director, singer, longtime activist, and, above all, acitizen of our great democracy. And as a citizen with a platform larger thanmost, I believe it is not only my right but also my duty to express myconcerns. So here goes Peter: I’m concerned by what I’m seeing in Pennsylvaniaand national Republicans’ ruthless efforts to unseat Bob Casey and flip thisbattleground red. If the GOP succeeds in flipping Pennsylvania red, they’llalmost certainly regain control of both the Senateand the White House,threatening everything from voting rights to women’s rights to the fightagainst climate change. That’s why outside interest groups have startedspending upwards of $150 million to defeat Bob. The stakes this November arehigher than ever before.So before I go on, can you please split a donationbetween Bob’s re-election campaign and Defeat Boebert PAC? DONATE NOW >> I’mcommitted to electing lawmakers like Bob Casey, who believes that everyonedeserves a fair shot at getting ahead and staying ahead. Bob’s opponent on theother hand is a Connecticut mega-millionaire who will do and say anything tohelp his own bottom line. With the most extreme Republican party of mylifetime teetering on the edge of regaining power, we need all hands on deck.If we’re going to protect our Senate majority and the White House, we must allstay informed and stay involved. So please, rush $25 or as much as you can toBob Casey and Defeat Boebert PAC right now to win in Pennsylvania. If you'vesaved your payment information with ActBlue Express, your weekly donation willgo through immediately: RUSH IN $25 RUSH IN $50 RUSH IN $100 RUSH IN $250RUSH IN $500 OTHER AMOUNT Thank you, Barbra DONATE Paid for by DefeatBoebert PAC This email was sent to dpwillis67@gmail.com .
